description: Bullet Protective Screens are the Most Durable Baseball Screens on the market. Protect your players and coaches with the most reliable baseball field screen on the market, the Bullet 10x10 Protective Screen. We have been Installing Sports Facilities for over 20+ years and know firsthand the abuse a Baseball Screen receives year-round. The durable design of the Bullet Protective Screen is ideal for high volume, and high-velocity training facilities. This Bullet Protective Screen comes fully equipped with a 10'H x 10'W square frame, 1 ⅝” industrial-grade galvanized steel frame, and #60 gauge nylon double-layered pillowcase netting. Built to withstand the constant abuse of a commercial training facility, high school, college, or organization, these screens are truly built to last. Match your team’s colors, reduce batted ball ricochet, and protect the life of your netting with heavy-duty foam and vinyl padding. Also, if you are needing a screen that is easy to move around, be sure to add our wheel kit that is perfect for both on and off the field.
